data.description: This exquisite neighborhood and the residence boasts three bedrooms and two bathrooms, nestled in a serene cul-de-sac, ensuring the tranquility and seclusion you desire. Upon entering, you'll be welcomed by an open-concept living area adorned with vaulted ceilings, creating a luminous and spacious ambiance. The generously sized kitchen is ideal for hosting gatherings, complemented by a charming kitchen nook for savoring your morning coffee. Step out onto the screened patio and revel in the allure of your secluded backyard, adorned with mature landscaping that contributes to a peaceful setting. The expansive master suite serves as a personal haven after a long day, featuring a roomy master bathroom equipped with a soothing jetted tub for ultimate relaxation.
